                                                <h3><strong><span>13. DISCLAIMER OF WARRANTIES</span></strong></h3>
                                                <p><span>13.1. We Provide QAPIN On “as Available”, “as Is”, And “with All Faults” Basis. To The Extent Permitted By The Applicable Law, We Do Not Make Any Representations Or Warranties About The Reliability, Suitability, And Accuracy, For Any Purpose, Of QAPIN, Any Content Featured On QAPIN, Whether Provider By Us Or By Third Parties, And Hereby Disclaim All Warranties Regarding QAPIN And Its Operation.</span></p>
